The '''Retribution''' was a popular model of [[Blaster carbine/Legends|blaster carbine]] that saw use during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was the preferred weapon of many [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] due to its light weight and quick response. The weapon's nickname was so popular, that it completely displaced the actual manufacturing designation.

